headline.print_headline: Republicans in Congress Plan Swift Action on Ambitious Agenda With Trump
headline.main: Republicans in Congress Plan Swift Action on Agenda With Donald Trump

snippet: Stunned by their good electoral fortunes, Republicans said they were eager to repeal the Affordable Care Act, cut taxes and confirm conservative judges....
